    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Astation is a modern digital game console that takes inspiration from the retro 999-in-1 cartridges. Dive into the world of Astation to discover a wide variety of games!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fighter Of Warped City</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is an old-school Beat 'em up game. Defeat enemies to progress and aim for the highest score.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/27f592494fda183aea2c7ebf7db75071.poster.avif?t=1762026790\" width=760 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/27f592494fda183aea2c7ebf7db75071.webm?t=1762026790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/27f592494fda183aea2c7ebf7db75071.mp4?t=1762026790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gothic Knight &amp; Creatures</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is an old-school action platformer game. Defeat your enemies to reach the end of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/8a086a86816f7ab0c3812e23a9f6eb62.poster.avif?t=1762026790\" width=760 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/8a086a86816f7ab0c3812e23a9f6eb62.webm?t=1762026790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/8a086a86816f7ab0c3812e23a9f6eb62.mp4?t=1762026790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TNT Man</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is an old-school  action game. Blast all your enemies and walls to win the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/b567d196a5ee150cf3e2f3b76c5afa5f.poster.avif?t=1762026790\" width=760 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/b567d196a5ee150cf3e2f3b76c5afa5f.webm?t=1762026790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3258880/extras/b567d196a5ee150cf3e2f3b76c5afa5f.mp4?t=1762026790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
